'''Abdel Hadi Mahbooba''' (d. 2005<ref name=nazikobit>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldbulletin.net/news_detail.php?id=5507 |work=World Bulletin |date=21 June 2007 |accessdate=24 June 2010 |title=Renowned Iraqi poet Nazik al-Malaika dies }}{{dead link|date=June 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>) was an [[Iraq]]i [[academic]]. He was the president of [[University of Basrah]] from 1964 to 1968.{{Citation needed|date=June 2010}} He was married to the Iraqi poet [[Nazik Al-Malaika]].<ref name=nazikobit />

